<h2>Our approach</h2>
<p>Resolve to Save Lives’ <a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/oq28g0ycisnk7nt/RTSL_CVD_Sodium%20Approach%20Fact%20Sheet_FINAL.pdf?dl=0">approach to salt reduction</a> aims to reduce the global intake of salt by 30% and is based on the World Health Organization’s <a href="https://www.who.int/dietphysicalactivity/publications/shake-salt-habit/en/">SHAKE Technical Package</a>.</p>

<p>We have identified a core set of salt reduction strategies, and work with countries to implement a strategy according to their key sources of salt, complementary efforts and political will.</p>

